  "about": {
    "title": "About Us",
    "missionTitle": "Mission",
    "missionText": "To provide excellent advice and service by offering our products to the hardware and construction sectors, under standards of variety, quality, and best price; satisfying the needs of our customers.",
    "visionTitle": "Vision",
    "visionText": "To be recognized as the leading company in the steel and hardware sector for our profitability, quality of products and services, in order to raise the standard of living of our workers.",
    "companyTitle": "Our Company",
    "companyText": "Founded in 1963 by Mr. Giovanni Ricupero Lombardi (deceased) and Mrs. María Stallone de Ricupero, established from the very beginning in the facilities we currently operate, Ciudad Bolívar, Bolívar State, with various renovations, expansions, and modernizations adapted over these more than 60 years.",
    "testimonialsTitle": "Testimonials",
    "testimonial1Text": "A solid strategic alliance has been developed over time between HIERROS RICUPERO, C.A. and our company BELIS GROUP, C.A. with the timely supply of high-quality materials at very competitive prices, which allows us to meet our main objective of strengthening the construction and design industry with the use of new technologies, meeting the requirements of our customers with the highest quality levels.",
    "testimonial1Author": "BELIS GROUP, C.A.",
    "testimonial2Text": "For the success of any Civil and Industrial Engineering project, it is important to have adequate and quality supplies. Constru Hierros Ricupero has provided us with the security and proper advice to ensure the fulfillment of activities, with maximum performance at the best cost in the shortest possible time. In this way, we have managed to create a competitive team, creating a bond of trust and security which is reflected in the great satisfaction of our customers.",
    "testimonial2Author": "Gregory Prieto, Engineer",
    "testimonial3Text": "The service offered by Constru-ir fills us with satisfaction as customers because it is characterized by its quick attention, the products have excellent price and quality, and above all, the pre-sale advice makes everything easier.",
    "testimonial3Author": "Antonio Lapadula, Constructora Arco"
  },
